[[Alone together - NEW]]
In the same way that Lisa Gitelman outlines the change in teaching with technology from blackboards to slides, we could examine the impact of social media on education. The increasing reliance on social media for information sharing and communication could potentially lead to a shift in teaching methods, incorporating more interactive and real-time discussions, as well as the use of multimedia content in the classroom.
